parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID for the Amazon Web Services account that contains the folder.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the folder.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: A display name for the folder.

nested_items.name: FolderType
nested_items.description: The type of folder it is.

nested_items.name: FolderPath
nested_items.description: An array of ancestor ARN strings for the folder.

nested_items.name: CreatedTime
nested_items.description: The time that the folder was created.

nested_items.name: LastUpdatedTime
nested_items.description: The time that the folder was last updated.

nested_items.description: The sharing scope of the folder.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.
